data.description:
Back on the market!  Turnkey, active, successful AirBNB duplex.  This building is beautiful and ready to go. One, one bedroom unit and one, two bedroom unit.  Great income stream the way it's being utilized now but also a great two unit rental or live in one, rent the other. Home could also easily convert to single family home.  Buy today, rent tomorrow or move in. 
Additional income possibility with the oversized two bay garage.  One of the bays has an oversized door for a large truck, boat or vehicle. Great for storage!  New roof in 2016 according to previous listing. 
Buyer to verify all information.
